<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.4.10">
<l>kolaikeḻu cemmu katta kaḷiṟoṉṟu koṉṟu koṭiyōṉi laṅkai poṭiyā</l>
<l>cilaikeḻu ceñca raṅkaḷ celavuytta naṅkaḷ tirumālai vēlai puṭaicūḻ</l>
<l>kalikeḻu māṭa vīti vayalmaṅkai maṉṉu kalikaṉṟi coṉṉa paṉuval</l>
<l>olikeḻu pāṭal pāṭi yuḻalkiṉṟa toṇṭa ravarāḷva rumpa rulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those devotees who wander, singing these resonant songs</l>
<l rend="indent">of the composition spoken by Kalikaṉṟi,</l>
<l>Who dwells in Maṅkai, with fields and streets of flourishing mansions</l>
<l rend="indent">with sugarcane on all sides,</l>
<l>About our Tirumāl who shot a bow to send bright, [fire] red arrows</l>
<l rend="indent">[to make] ash of the evil one’s Laṅkā,</l>
<l>Having killed a bright, red-faced, vicious elephant,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will rule the heavenly world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
